    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1930-08-22T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1930-08-22T00:00:00-05:00" n="754"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d754">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">871.014 Bessarabia/128</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Rumanian Minister</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Davila</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <p>The Roumanian Minister presents his compliments to the Secretary of State, and
                    has the honour to request him to be good enough to let him have a reply to his
                        <hi rend="italic">aide-mémoire</hi> of February 18th, concerning the status
                    of Roumanian citizens born in Bessarabia.</p>
                <closer>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1930-08-22">August 22,
                            1930</date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
                <postscript>
                    <p>No. 3650/P–8</p>
                </postscript>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
